<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>What We Do</h1>
    <p class="lead">From building software from scratch to bringing crashed servers back to life</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services-detail">
  <div class="container">
    {% for service in services %}
    <div class="service-detail" style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <span style="font-size: 2.5rem;">{{ service.icon }}</span>
        <h2 style="margin: 0;">{{ service.title }}</h2>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">{{ service.description }}</p>
      <p style="color: var(--text-color); line-height: 1.8;">{{ service.details }}</p>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-content" style="background: var(--light-bg); padding: 3rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">How We Work</h2>
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3>1. Initial Chat</h3>
        <p>Tell us what you need. We'll ask questions to understand your situation and goals.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3>2. Proposal</h3>
        <p>We'll outline what we can do, how long it'll take, and what it'll cost. No hidden fees, no surprises.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3>3. Get It Done</h3>
        <p>We do the work, keep you updated, and deliver what we promised. Regular communication, no radio silence.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3>4. Support</h3>
        <p>We stick around to make sure everything works as expected. Questions? Changes? We're here.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to Start?</h2>
    <p>Let's talk about your project or technical challenge.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
  </div>
</section>
